The system performance will be improved further when a larger size of the LDPC matrix combined with the proposed interleaving is used. Fig. 7 shows the performance of the system when a large size of LDPC matrix 32406480, corresponding to the Z = 270 gap is used. As a result, as much as 970 burst error bits can be corrected with the BER of 10-4.

